Package: PValuator
Title: Package for determining the optimal p-value using mathematical methods
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alexandre", "Boullé", , "alexandre.boulle@ijm.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The methods (Euclidean distance, geometry of Bézier curves) aim to determine the area where the curvature of the curve representing the number of values obtained as a function of the p-value is most pronounced.
